{"tid":2362392,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"〔真人故事〕岩岩男朋友教我渣車點知。。。","createTime":"2021-01-11T11:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T12:38:29.000Z","uid":382981,"like":2,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7c67c6c30f53920679c0acefa096b690e577b6","tid":2362392,"uid":382981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:49:23.000Z","msg":"話說我早幾日就考到車牌<br />\n咁就緊係車我男友豬豬出去玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知我唔識路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />電話又收唔到用唔到ｇｏｏｇｌｅｍａｐ<br />\n於是就叫我男友教我行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開始都好地地 點知教教下佢竟然話<br />\n<br />\n男友：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男友：「架車行右呀」<br />\n我：「ＯＫ」（轉右）<br />\n男友：「車行右呀」<br />\n我：「ＯＫ」（轉右）<br />\n男友：「一路直行」<br />\n我：「ＯＫ」（直行）<br />\n男友：「車行左呀」<br />\n我：「ＯＫ」（轉左）<br />\n男友：「你做咩轉左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n我：「你叫我行左嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n男友：「我話我扯行左呀！！！」<br />\n我：「＆＊！＠％＆＃＊︿＠！（＄＆＄」"},{"pid":"a28354ba54a9dba1c3964765be63b9848caa2a81","tid":2362392,"uid":382981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:50:01.000Z","msg":"大家話佢過唔過份 渣緊車搵咁既野黎講笑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e423ca58245a6668af73a485053e0de938f8c58","tid":2362392,"uid":198764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆"},{"pid":"a9